There's a high cost to adding a new element. If the use case is already served by &lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;, and there isn't huge benefit from &lt;blockcode&gt;, then it's not worth it.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4">zcorpan</a> — Thu Mar 31, 2011 7:37 pm</p><hr />
