<title type="html"><![CDATA[Blockcode tag]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/viewtopic.php?t=4311&amp;p=5921#p5921"><![CDATA[
I would like if they added the <dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>blockcode</code></dd></dl> tag as a shortcut for <dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;</code></dd></dl>. It's the same quantity of characters, but a single tag is less cumberstome.<br /><br />Is said that is not going to be added because is &quot;not backwards compatible with previous specs&quot;, but there's also many new elements that aren't supported by earlier browsers; and both inline and block elements with different CSS properties.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=523">peroyomas</a> — Wed May 26, 2010 2:16 pm</p><hr />
